<para style="q1">

<verse number="12" style="v" />Troubles that cannot be numbered surround me;</para>

<para style="q1">my iniquities have caught up with me so that I am no longer able to see anything;</para>

<para style="q1">they are more than the hairs on my head,</para>

<para style="q1">and my heart has failed me.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />Be pleased, Yahweh, to rescue me;</para>

<para style="q1">hurry to help me, Yahweh.</para>
